IT_-Dimitrios-Kambouris_Getty-Images-for-WSJ.-Magazine-Innovators-Awards-and-Arturo-Holmes_MG23_Getty-Images-for-The-Met-Museum_Vogue-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “被人看见的感觉真是太棒了，我不认为这是理所当然的”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/questlove-thanks-kendrick-lamar-for-referencing-the-roots-in-squabble-up-video-teases-new-roots-album-3817026">Questlove 的帖子感谢肯德里克·拉马尔 (Kendrick Lamar) 在“Squabble Up”视频中引用了 Roots，并预告新的 Roots 专辑</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Questlove-and-Kendrick-Lamar.-CREDIT_-Dimitrios-Kambouris_Getty-Images-for-WSJ.-Magazine-Innovators-Awards-and-Arturo-Holmes_MG23_Getty-Images-for-The-Met-Museum_Vogue.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Questlove-and-Kendrick-Lamar.-CREDIT_-Dimitrios-Kambouris_Getty-Images-for-WSJ.-Magazine-Innovators-Awards-and-Arturo-Holmes_MG23_Getty-Images-for-The-Met-Museum_Vogue.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Questlove-and-Kendrick-Lamar.-CREDIT_-Dimitrios-Kambouris_Getty-Images-for-WSJ.-Magazine-Innovators-Awards-and-Arturo-Holmes_MG23_Getty-Images-for-The-Met-Museum_Vogue-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Questlove-and-Kendrick-Lamar.-CREDIT_-Dimitrios-Kambouris_Getty-Images-for-WSJ.-Magazine-Innovators-Awards-and-Arturo-Holmes_MG23_Getty-Images-for-The-Met-Museum_Vogue-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Questlove-and-Kendrick-Lamar.-CREDIT_-Dimitrios-Kambouris_Getty-Images-for-WSJ.-Magazine-Innovators-Awards-and-Arturo-Holmes_MG23_Getty-Images-for-The-Met-Museum_Vogue-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Questlove-and-Kendrick-Lamar.-CREDIT_-Dimitrios-Kambouris_Getty-Images-for-WSJ.-Magazine-Innovators-Awards-and-Arturo-Holmes_MG23_Getty-Images-for-The-Met-Museum_Vogue-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Questlove-and-Kendrick-Lamar.-CREDIT_-Dimitrios-Kambouris_Getty-Images-for-WSJ.-Magazine-Innovators-Awards-and-Arturo-Holmes_MG23_Getty-Images-for-The-Met-Museum_Vogue-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/questlove">Questlove</a>感谢肯德里克<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kendrick-lamar">·拉马尔 (Kendrick Lamar)</a>在《Squabble Up》的音乐视频中引用了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-roots">Roots 乐队</a>，同时还预告了该乐队的新专辑。 </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="706" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/kendrick-lamar-gnx-review-3815647">肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）——“GNX”评论：将仇恨变成可教的时刻</a></b></li></ul><p>拉马尔于周五（11 月 22 日）毫无预警地发行了他的第六张专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/kendrick-lamar-gnx-review-3815647">GNX</a> 》，这是他自 2022 年的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/kendrick-lamar-mr-morale-and-the-big-steppers-3225059#:~:text=Overall%2C%20'Mr%20Morale%20%26%20The,tone%20over%20dark%20guitar%20gargles.">Mr. Morale &amp; The Big Steppers</a> 》以来的首张专辑。它由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jack-antonoff">Jack Antonoff</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kamasi-washington">Kamasi Washington</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mustard">Mustard</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/terrace-martin">Terrace Martin</a>和 Sounwave 制作，还包括来自<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sza">SZA</a>的未署名客串演唱。</p><p>然后，本周早些时候，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-kendrick-lamar-celebrate-compton-in-new-video-for-squabble-up-3815732">分享了由 Calmatic 执导的《Squabble Up》的视觉效果</a>，而不是拉马尔的频繁创意合作伙伴戴夫·弗里 (Dave Free)。故事发生在一个几乎空荡荡的舞厅里，演员们轮流跳舞，其中包括拉马尔本人。</p><p>粉丝们很快注意到该视频的场景与 The Roots 1999 年的单曲“The Next Movement”中使用的场景非常相似，现在 Questlove 站出来表示敬意。 </p><p><iframe title="根源 - 下一个运动" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qm7Xt2Qsjcg?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>他在 Instagram 上写道，感谢肯德里克强调了该团体历史上的一个时刻，他认为“没有人看到或关心”。</p><p> “我曾经开玩笑说，在我的生活中，有人只是因为 Hanes 的广告才认识乔丹，”他继续说道。 “我承认我是几十年来隐藏在众目睽睽之下的国王，我们生活在我们为自己设定的现实中。”</p><p> “然而……我最喜欢的是我在@TheRoots 中创作的音乐——这是我的火焰的燃料，有时如果你喜欢某样东西，你就必须让它自由。然后，如果它返回给你，它就是真实的。也就是说，我要感谢@kendricklamar 承认了一些我认为没有人看到或关心的事情。被人看见的感觉真是太棒了，我不认为这是理所当然的。”</p><p>然后他补充道：“是的，新专辑还在推出，哈哈。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DC1yuIRRIjS/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 